Video:
The video explaining the idea and including the demonstration is uploaded to youtube. Please use the following link:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pgsPrW6pFMU&feature=youtube_gdata

Steps to recreate the demo:
Please download the zip-file 'template_apache-spark-demo-master.zip' and 
open the main class by navigating through the levels (project dist-data-spark --> iotprojectspark --> SparkIoT.java)
and run the SparkIoT class. The SparkIoT class that contains the main class is also using the UserInfo.java class that
can be found in the same package. 

Links:
Sparks and code used from lectures and examples given

